examples.en: It's unlawful to drive without a license.
It's unlawful to try to duck out of paying taxes.
The question arose as to whether this behaviour was unlawful.
The sale of alcohol to minors is unlawful.
They had entered the country by unlawful means.
...it is unlawful to set off fireworks within the city limits...
She filed an action for unlawful detainer of land after nonpayment of rent.
